 precious metals, research, advisory, and capital markets services to institutional, corporate, financial sponsor, and Global Wealth Management customers, as well as focused rates and credit platform. The company also offers lending products, such as securities-based lending, mortgages, structured products, and tailored solutions; collateralized lending residential and commercial real estate, primarily against securities, residential and commercial real estate, other real assets (such as ships and aircraft), private market and hedge fund interest; and unsecured lending. The company was formerly known as UBS AG and changed its name to UBS Group AG in December 2014. UBS Group AG was founded in 1862 and is headquartered in Zurich, Switzerland.","industry":"Banks - Diversified","sector":"Financial Services","marketCap":157301866496,"trailingPE":17.200718,"forwardPE":11.766927,"pegRatio":0.57,"priceToBook":1.6145203,"priceToSales":3.0656557,"profitMargin":17.764,"operatingMargin":31.471002,"grossMargin":0,"returnOnEquity":10.16,"returnOnAssets":0.567,"revenueGrowthYoy":13.8,"earningsGrowthYoy":84.39999999999999,"earningsQuarterlyGrowthYoy":79.7,"debtToEquity":null,"currentRatio":null,"quickRatio":null,"freeCashFlow":null,"operatingCashFlow":null,"totalCash":528411983872,"totalDebt":574302978048,"revenue":51311001600,"dividendYield":2.29,"payoutRatio":32.259998,"beta":0.831,"fiftyTwoWeekHigh":49.36,"fiftyTwoWeekLow":30.36,"targetMeanPrice":49.26667,"targetHighPrice":61.8,"targetLowPrice":42,"recommendationKey":"buy","numberOfAnalystOpinions":3,"lastQuarter":{"date":"2026-03-31","period":"-1q","epsActual":0.9506,"epsEstimate":0.82743,"surprisePct":14.89},"earningsHistory":[{"date":"2025-06-30","period":"-4q","epsActual":0.8226,"epsEstimate":0.92276,"surprisePct":-10.850000399999999},{"date":"2025-09-30","period":"-3q","epsActual":0.9179,"epsEstimate":0.60424,"surprisePct":51.910000000000004},{"date":"2025-12-31","period":"-2q","epsActual":0.6702,"epsEstimate":0.67459,"surp